{"type": "article", "id": 7186, "title": "Fujiyama Glass 富士山酒杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-09T07:35:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234111jGvJIOMexdR0zhnE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本人对富士山的爱真是体现在各种细小的设计中。近期，设计师 keita suzuki 做了一款小酒杯。这个看上去平平无奇的小酒杯一旦被倒入啤酒，上层泛起啤酒特有的泡沫，就会和下部的颜色以及形状共同构成富士山的模样。不管倒入什么颜色的啤酒，杯子的通透性都会让你看到不同颜色的美妙，好似一场和富士山甜蜜的邂逅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234109sbYx3Mt8ImZ49ozD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523410904AU25MZeXSlLOaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234110sMxKgcPJjutzrQO8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234110cw703VSiHQTpvben.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}